<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今天的突破性故事|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com是您最新的中国新闻报道和时事的在线来源</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 09:15:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国说，这反对特朗普的加沙收购建议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-it-opposes-trumps-gaza-takeover-proposal-2025-02-06/</link><description>中国外交部周四表示，北京反对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）将巴勒斯坦人从加沙（Gaza）转移到加沙（Gaza），并让美国接管该地区。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 08:51:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-it-opposes-trumps-gaza-takeover-proposal-2025-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>当地媒体报道</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-giant-byd-hire-20000-zhengzhou-q1-local-media-reports-2025-02-06/</link><description>政府经营的Henan Daily周四报道，中国电动汽车制造商BYD计划在第一季度在郑州雇用20,000名员工，包括研发和制造业，包括R＆D和制造业。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 08:31:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-giant-byd-hire-20000-zhengzhou-q1-local-media-reports-2025-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>克里姆林宫解雇了俄罗斯航天局的老板</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/kremlin-fires-boss-russias-space-agency-2025-02-06/</link><description>克里姆林宫周四撤离了俄罗斯航天局的负责人，这是不到三年的任期，这是由于俄罗斯在47年内首次向月球任务的巨大失败而伤痕累累的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 08:28:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/kremlin-fires-boss-russias-space-agency-2025-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯的Sberbank计划与中国联合AI研究，因为DeepSeek跳过</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/russias-sberbank-plans-joint-ai-research-with-china-deepseek-leaps-forward-2025-02-06/</link><description>俄罗斯最大银行的高管告诉路透社，Sberbank计划与中国研究人员在联合AI项目上合作，因为中国的DeepSeek通过创建AI模型比美国竞争对手更便宜地颠覆了技术格局。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 08:22:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/russias-sberbank-plans-joint-ai-research-with-china-deepseek-leaps-forward-2025-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普的de minimis取消对temu来说是个坏消息，但对Shein来说更糟糕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/trumps-de-minimis-cancellation-is-bad-news-temu-worse-shein-2025-02-06/</link><description>特朗普政府采取行动停止进入美国免税的低成本进口，这可能会比Temu的更广泛的产品系列更大，并且更改其运输策略，这可能比在线美元商店Temu更加严重。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 08:19:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/trumps-de-minimis-cancellation-is-bad-news-temu-worse-shein-2025-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>DeepSeek发烧燃料中国人工智能股票的爱国赌注</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/deepseek-fever-fuels-patriotic-bets-chinese-ai-stocks-2025-02-06/</link><description>中国投资者正在赶紧与AI相关的股票，押注本土初创公司DeepSeek的人工智能进步将导致该行业的繁荣，并在一场加强的中国技术战争中向中国发动了主动性。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 08:14:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/deepseek-fever-fuels-patriotic-bets-chinese-ai-stocks-2025-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国，巴基斯坦保证促进基础设施合作，采矿项目</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-pakistan-pledge-boost-cooperation-infrastructure-mining-projects-2025-02-06/</link><description>官方官方报道，中国和巴基斯坦将升级和重建巴基斯坦的铁路网络，并进一步发展其瓜达尔港口，而中国公司可以在南亚国家的海上石油和天然气发展中进行投资。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 08:12:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-pakistan-pledge-boost-cooperation-infrastructure-mining-projects-2025-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国商务部说，美国关税“卑鄙”，“单方面”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-commerce-ministry-says-us-tariffs-vile-unilateralist-2025-02-06/</link><description>中国商务部周四表示，在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统威胁要对美国主要贸易伙伴签署进口关税之后，美国关税是“邪恶的”，“单方面”，并加剧了全球贸易紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 07:58:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-commerce-ministry-says-us-tariffs-vile-unilateralist-2025-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国名字好斗外交官作为欧洲高级特使</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-names-lu-shaye-special-representative-european-affairs-2025-02-06/</link><description>中国外交部周四表示，中国已任命有争议的外交官和前巴萨德，卢·沙耶（Lu Shaye）为欧洲事务特别代表。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 07:44:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-names-lu-shaye-special-representative-european-affairs-2025-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>焦点：中国的美国乙烷进口量在2025年激增，以削减成本</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-us-ethane-imports-surge-2025-drive-cut-costs-2025-02-06/</link><description>尽管华盛顿和北京之间发生了贸易战的日益增长，但中国从美国进口的埃塞内斯（Ethane）今年仍将激增，因为与缩水利润作斗争的大型石化生产商转向了从美国页岩气繁荣流动的较便宜的原料。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 07:40:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-us-ethane-imports-surge-2025-drive-cut-costs-2025-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股票在一月份看到尖锐的外国流出</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/asian-equities-see-sharp-foreign-outflows-january-2025-02-06/</link><description>一月份，外国投资者大量从亚洲股票中撤出，受到美国国债收益率较高的限制，并引起人们对区域出口可能遭受唐纳德·特朗普总统政府额外关税的担忧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 07:17:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/asian-equities-see-sharp-foreign-outflows-january-2025-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>在DeepSeek飞跃之后，俄罗斯的Sberbank计划与中国联合AI研究</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/after-deepseek-leap-forward-russias-sberbank-plans-joint-ai-research-with-china-2025-02-06/</link><description>一位高管告诉路透社，俄罗斯最大的银行Sberbank计划与中国研究人员在联合AI项目上合作，因为DeepSeek通过创建强大的AI模型比美国竞争对手更便宜地颠覆了技术格局。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 07:15:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/after-deepseek-leap-forward-russias-sberbank-plans-joint-ai-research-with-china-2025-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国调查更新放心，阿斯利康的股票上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-2025-sales-outlook-tops-expectations-2025-02-06/</link><description>阿斯利康（Astrazeneca）股票周四上涨，此前这位制药商表示可能面临中国最高450万美元的罚款，而对于两种癌症药物的无薪进口税，对分析师的未付进口税，并使投资者表示业务影响很小。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 07:10:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-2025-sales-outlook-tops-expectations-2025-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>饮料制造商Pernod削减了对中国外观不佳的销售预测</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/drinks-group-pernod-cuts-2025-sales-outlook-challenges-us-china-2025-02-06/</link><description>法国饮料公司Pernod Ricard周四削减了2025年和长期前景，理由是中国的市场条件，特别是对于Martell Cognac品牌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 06:52:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/drinks-group-pernod-cuts-2025-sales-outlook-challenges-us-china-2025-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>尽管中国订单延迟</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/siemens-healthineers-reports-q1-revenue-slightly-above-consensus-2025-02-06/</link><description>德国医疗技术公司西门子卫生厂周四报告说，第一季度收入略高于共识，市场开放率上涨了5.5％，因为其美国收入增长了16％，而来自中国的收入则下降了6％，因为“客户订单的延迟延迟”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 06:14:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/siemens-healthineers-reports-q1-revenue-slightly-above-consensus-2025-02-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>